=========================
Help - Coding Conventions
=========================

1. Variable Naming
-------------------
All variable names should be preceded by a prefix, indicating its type, as shown in the following table:
==================================
      Type      |    Prefix  
==================================
     simple     |      v_*
----------------------------------
   structure    |      s_*
----------------------------------
      cell      |      c_*
----------------------------------
   constants,   |
    indices     |   no prefix
----------------------------------
(where * stands for the variable name) 

2. File Naming
--------------
All files created inside a project should be named with the following prefixes:
==================================
     Type       |    Prefix  
==================================
     script     |      s*
----------------------------------
    function    |      f*
----------------------------------
      help      |     help_*
----------------------------------
(where * stands for the file name) 